{"tid":891462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【三藩市直擊】美國中期選舉在即 華人：浪費時間","createTime":"2018-11-06T06:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T11:53:35.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d4170162f22c7a1c748671874d36cfbd62fab7e0","tid":891462,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"美國時間明日（11月6日）是國會中期選舉，選舉被喻為總統與執政黨的「期中考試」，大部份國會議員將面臨選民對他們任職兩年來的評價。移民、女權、醫保議題是這次選舉最大關注點，尤其在傳出特朗普計劃廢除出生公民權之後，移民問題已不僅限於無證移民，亦可能影響合法公民的取得途徑。不過，在美華人是否感覺到這股緊張感呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181106/small/1541477933_ea5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181106%2Fsmall%2F1541477933_ea5d.jpg&h=b578e5b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位年輕人表示身為美國公民，有義務投票。<br />\n記者在三藩市灣區訪問華人，是否知道11月6日是選舉日，年長受訪者的答案「不知道」居多。有人直言「不理會這些事」、「選舉是浪費時間，誰執政都是一樣」。對於特朗普的政策，不反對也不支持。<br />\n<br />\n知道明日是選舉日的，多數是年輕人。一位沒有投票權的華裔女性居民表示，如果她有權投票，會支持特朗普；她指出，「比如說美國非法移民，去監控這個，我覺得是有它的道理在。」<br />\n<br />\n另一位有投票權的24歲青年認為，特朗普使用過激言詞，很懂得迎合選民喜好，以便緊緊抓住基本盤；但其施政帶有分裂性，似乎沒有要團結美國人的意圖。他表示會去投票，因為那是公民義務，民主社會中的公民應該要參與。  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181106/58879642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F58879642&d=uhKk4%2BaM5TcFbhkeqGl3ITA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e1f637d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F58879642&h=1e999d37\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181106/58879642</a>"},{"pid":"b7f2e16a8dd3573c2aabc30ea4da4e1afce63cc2","tid":891462,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識玩 知識自己係二等公民"},{"pid":"8d4b21c7cbd5c5556846320a43fb4460c40d1fff","tid":891462,"uid":2795,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:26:18.000Z","msg":"投白票 連登仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3b9ba62bedd6806b77a5bc5d0ffa27290019c0","tid":891462,"uid":53687,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"即刻出條法案趕你走，仲睇下係咪浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5755fb0be73427a6a2d7a67899a49c1ac1e04d","tid":891462,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:32:40.000Z","msg":"有乜出奇<br />\n反正都唔會選咗個略自己水既總統<br />\n畀我都唔理"},{"pid":"573c7a1e7fd21c39bdf16dd326e82cab3dd19700","tid":891462,"uid":810,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:49:27.000Z","msg":"華人去到邊都係各家自掃門前雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a35450dc5f6f90ee34e1c1e0415ba7f85a1cf0d","tid":891462,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n共和定民主黨都針對緊支那<br />\n唔鍾意咪走囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39660dde6be5291132bd9e194d082a714bbc9d5","tid":891462,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"幾時會再出現全球排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16745d66f44dd906802672607de7cd8cb08760e3","tid":891462,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"拎張票印個fuck字"},{"pid":"9c13c8dbcbfd8d84f114b094c3055e693c357ea5","tid":891462,"uid":120678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:05:41.000Z","msg":"澳洲唔投票要罰錢<br />\n美國應該冇相關規定"},{"pid":"15f45ea83e71094b522a0443629b1787431a997a","tid":891462,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"典型廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":